HomePage.title: Welcome! Here is your 'not so local' tech handyman speaking!
HomePage.content introduction: Welcome to my personnal website. Here you may find many tools and informations I find handy. I may have crafted one or two of them and am very much willing to have feedbacks on, if you took the time to try them out, or even to look at the code. I am a software engineer selling his services as a Jack of all trades. I know about datastructures, storage, continuous deployment over private custom servers, and web-design for a good user experience.Important features for good referencement (see SEO field inside the ressource section of this website). I also come with the softskills you need as I will make sure you are part of the architecture and design process (if you don't already come up with a design and are willing to take this time).
HomePage.catchphrase: Why looking for a team of 5 people who will spend time aguing and transmitt informations back and forth when you can hire the 10x web-master who will do a better structured job in less time?
